tart of its next turn.</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Success</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Creatures take half damage but do not fall prone.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Synergy</strong>: If you have an affinity to other infusions, you can enhance the bead. A bead can only withstand one synergy.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Aerofusion </strong>empowers the explosion. All creatures within the area of the explosion have disadvantage on their saving throw. In addition, creatures that are Huge or smaller are knocked prone regardless of the result of the saving throw (unless the creature is immune to being knocked prone).</li>\n<li><strong>Bloodfusion </strong>creates a toxic gas, sickening all creatures within the area of the explosion. Creatures are sickened, regardless of the result of the saving throw, and have a 1d4 penalty to all saving throws, ability checks, and attacks for 1 minute.</li>\n<li><strong>Hydrofusion </strong>turns your explosion of flames into a substance similar to lava. The ground affected by the explosion becomes difficult terrain and any creature entering an affected space or begins its turn in one takes 1d4 fire damage.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"HD: 4, Somatic"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":30,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":100,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["10d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"requirements":"Pyrofusist","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DI11opiBN9KroioG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZBLLKU3s8ONoFweA","name":"Flame Blade","type":"feat","img":"systems/pergashaFoundryvtt/icons/pergasha_icons/infusion_pyro.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Fire motes gather in your free hand, forming a fiery blade similar in size and shape to a scimitar, and it lasts for the duration. If you let go of the blade, it disappears, but you can gather the motes into the blade again as a bonus action.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><br />You can make a fusion melee attack with the fiery blade. On a hit, the target takes 1d8 plus 1 point per Fireweaving tier in fire damage. The blade is immaterial, so Strength and Dexterity modifiers do not affect the damage. The blade sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet. It can also ignite combustible materials such as parchment, straw, dry sticks, and cloth.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Empower</strong>: </span>You can spend up to 2 additional mana when triggering this ability to increase the damage of the flame blade by 1d8 per mana.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Synergy</strong>: If you have an affinity to other infusions, you can enhance the blade. Your blade can only use one synergy at a time, but you can change the synergy at will once per turn.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Aerofusion </strong>extends the reach of your blade by 5 feet. On a critical hit, you add slashing damage equal to your Constitution modifier.</li>\n<li><strong>Bloodfusion </strong>adds a sickening edge to your blade, dealing necrotic damage equal to your Constitution modifier on a successful hit. On a critical hit, you absorb vitality from your foe and regain Hit Points equal to your Constitution modifier.</li>\n<li><strong>Hydrofusion </strong>causes your blade to splash flames at nearby creatures. On a hit, you can allow the flames to lash out at any number of creatures of your choice that are adjacent to your target, dealing fire damage equal to your Constitution modifier. On a critical hit, your target takes additional piercing damage equal to your Constitution modifier.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"Mana: 2-4, Somatic"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+1","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"psionics"},"requirements":"Pyrofusist","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DI11opiBN9KroioG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZBLLKU3s8ONoFweA","name":"Flame Blade","type":"feat","img":"systems/pergashaFoundryvtt/icons/pergasha_icons/infusion_pyro.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Fire motes gather in your free hand, forming a fiery blade similar in size and shape to a scimitar, and it lasts for the duration. If you let go of the blade, it disappears, but you can gather the motes into the blade again as a bonus action.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><br />You can make a fusion melee attack with the fiery blade. On a hit, the target takes 1d8 plus 1 point per Fireweaving tier in fire damage. The blade is immaterial, so Strength and Dexterity modifiers do not affect the damage. The blade sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet. It can also ignite combustible materials such as parchment, straw, dry sticks, and cloth.</span></p>\n<p><br /><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Empower</strong>: </span>You can spend up to 2 additional mana when triggering this ability to increase the damage of the flame blade by 1d8 per mana.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Synergy</strong>: If you have an affinity to other infusions, you can enhance the blade. Your blade can only use one synergy at a time, but you can change the synergy at will once per turn.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Aerofusion </strong>extends the reach of your blade by 5 feet. On a critical hit, you add slashing damage equal to your Constitution modifier.</li>\n<li><strong>Bloodfusion </strong>adds a sickening edge to your blade, dealing necrotic damage equal to your Constitution modifier on a successful hit. On a critical hit, you absorb vitality from your foe and regain Hit Points equal to your Constitution modifier.</li>\n<li><strong>Hydrofusion </strong>causes your blade to splash flames at nearby creatures. On a hit, you can allow the flames to lash out at any number of creatures of your choice that are adjacent to your target, dealing fire damage equal to your Constitution modifier. On a critical hit, your target takes additional piercing damage equal to your Constitution modifier.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"Mana: 2-4, Somatic"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+1","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"psionics"},"requirements":"Pyrofusist","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DI11opiBN9KroioG":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"T8JiXopc9r3ajRKT","name":"Flame Arrows Tier 1","type":"feat","img":"systems/pergashaFoundryvtt/icons/pergasha_icons/infusion_pyro.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Fire motes transform ammunition (such as arrows, crossbow bolts, and sling stones) into fiery projectiles. Each piece of ammunition deals an extra 1d6 points of fire damage to any target it hits. A flaming projectile can easily ignite a flammable object or structure, but it won't ignite a creature it strikes. </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Empower</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">While this ability is active, you can use a bonus action and spend 1 mana to turn your shot into a burst. Your shot deals damage as normal but also creates a burst of fire. All creatures within 10 feet of your target must make a Dexterity save or take 1d6 fire damage per Fireweaving tier you have mastered. </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>Success</strong>: </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Creatures take half damage.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Synergy</strong>: If you have an affinity to other infusions, you can enhance your flame arrows. Your arrows can only use one synergy at a time, but you can change the synergy at will once per turn.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Aerofusion adds slicing wings of wind to your ammunition, adding 1 slashing damage per Windweaving or Fireweaving tier you have mastered, taking the highest value.</li>\n<li>Bloodfusion grants a blood-hungry aspect to your ammunition. Whenever you miss your target while using a flame arrow, you can reroll the attack. Otherwise on a hit, roll an attack against an additional creature within 30 feet of your original target. On a success, your flame arrow pierces through the first target and into the next, dealing necrotic damage equal to your Constitution modifier. (You cannot use this ability if your original attack was a miss.)</li>\n<li>Hydrofusion strengthens the ammunition, increasing the damage added to 1d8 instead. This increase also affects the Empower ability of this infusion.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":"HD: 1, Somatic"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d6","fire"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"dex","dc":null,"scaling":"con"},"requirements":"Pyrofusist","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DI11opiBN9KroioG":3},"flags":{}}
